{
  "video_id": "fscaRh2OtXk",
  "title": "Science didn't understand my kids' rare disease until I decided to study it | Sharon Terry",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12260.0,
      "end_time": 15396.0,
      "text": "The best Christmas my children ever had"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15420.0,
      "end_time": 18740.0,
      "text": "was also the worst Christmas my husband and I ever had."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19620.0,
      "end_time": 21436.0,
      "text": "Elizabeth, age seven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21460.0,
      "end_time": 24316.0,
      "text": "and her brother, Ian, age five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24340.0,
      "end_time": 28590.0,
      "text": "couldn&#39;t imagine why they were getting everything they wanted for Christmas."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29600.0,
      "end_time": 31779.0,
      "text": "The reason Santa was so generous"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32580.0,
      "end_time": 35836.0,
      "text": "was because of something my husband Pat and I knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35860.0,
      "end_time": 37700.0,
      "text": "and the kids couldn&#39;t comprehend."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41420.0,
      "text": "Something that we had just learned, and it terrified us."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43380.0,
      "end_time": 45636.0,
      "text": "This was 1994"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45660.0,
      "end_time": 48190.0,
      "text": "and the story actually starts a few years earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48620.0,
      "end_time": 53419.0,
      "text": "For a couple of years I had noticed a rash on the sides of Elizabeth&#39;s neck"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54220.0,
      "end_time": 55699.0,
      "text": "that looked like prickly heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56780.0,
      "end_time": 60660.0,
      "text": "For those same years, my father and brother both died of cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61420.0,
      "end_time": 64100.0,
      "text": "and I was probably overanxious about illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64940.0,
      "end_time": 67716.0,
      "text": "The doctors assured us there was nothing wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67740.0,
      "end_time": 69476.0,
      "text": "and I shouldn&#39;t worry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69500.0,
      "end_time": 70900.0,
      "text": "but I wasn&#39;t so sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72200.0,
      "end_time": 75116.0,
      "text": "And so without a referral, and paying out-of-pocket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75140.0,
      "end_time": 77339.0,
      "text": "I took Elizabeth to a dermatologist."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78380.0,
      "end_time": 80716.0,
      "text": "She was probably just allergic to something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80740.0,
      "end_time": 85140.0,
      "text": "but why did it appear just on the sides of her neck, this rash?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86660.0,
      "end_time": 88596.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s two days before Christmas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88620.0,
      "end_time": 89820.0,
      "text": "1994,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91200.0,
      "end_time": 94396.0,
      "text": "and the dermatologist takes a quick look at her neck and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94420.0,
      "end_time": 96460.0,
      "text": "\"She has pseudoxanthoma elasticum.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97460.0,
      "end_time": 101590.0,
      "text": "And then he shuts off the lights and looks in her eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102140.0,
      "end_time": 103796.0,
      "text": "It turns out, by chance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103820.0,
      "end_time": 106940.0,
      "text": "this dermatologist also trained in ophthalmology."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107900.0,
      "end_time": 109100.0,
      "text": "Our lucky day."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111220.0,
      "end_time": 112980.0,
      "text": "I am sick to my stomach."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113460.0,
      "end_time": 114716.0,
      "text": "\"Oma?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114740.0,
      "end_time": 117636.0,
      "text": "Oma&#39;s like melanoma, lymphoma --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117660.0,
      "end_time": 118860.0,
      "text": "cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119660.0,
      "end_time": 123396.0,
      "text": "\"Why are you looking in her eyes for a skin rash?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123420.0,
      "end_time": 125500.0,
      "text": "I scream and make no sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126540.0,
      "end_time": 127740.0,
      "text": "So there it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128620.0,
      "end_time": 132180.0,
      "text": "Elizabeth has pseudoxanthoma elasticum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 134820.0,
      "text": "PXE for short."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136700.0,
      "end_time": 138995.0,
      "text": "Questions mix with fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139200.0,
      "end_time": 141220.0,
      "text": "and erupt like bile in my throat."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141739.0,
      "end_time": 143460.0,
      "text": "Why are you looking in her eyes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144660.0,
      "end_time": 147636.0,
      "text": "What do you know about this? How do you know for sure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147660.0,
      "end_time": 149140.0,
      "text": "What is the prognosis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 153740.0,
      "text": "My training in pastoral counseling did not prepare me for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155500.0,
      "end_time": 159380.0,
      "text": "Dr. Bercovitch tells us everything he knows about PXE."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160660.0,
      "end_time": 162420.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a rare genetic disorder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163620.0,
      "end_time": 164820.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s systemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165860.0,
      "end_time": 169780.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a slowly progressing, premature aging disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170660.0,
      "end_time": 174220.0,
      "text": "It causes loose wrinkly skin in the flexor areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 175420.0,
      "end_time": 177356.0,
      "text": "It causes legal blindness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177380.0,
      "end_time": 179100.0,
      "text": "like macular degeneration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179780.0,
      "end_time": 182500.0,
      "text": "and a host of cardiovascular problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 183500.0,
      "end_time": 185580.0,
      "text": "Little is known about this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186420.0,
      "end_time": 189236.0,
      "text": "and some people die in their 30s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191739.0,
      "text": "say some of the reports at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196600.0,
      "text": "He then just glances at our son and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197940.0,
      "end_time": 199140.0,
      "text": "\"He has it, too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201220.0,
      "end_time": 206600.0,
      "text": "We want to flee back to the land of normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 210740.0,
      "end_time": 212156.0,
      "text": "Two days after Christmas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212180.0,
      "end_time": 215196.0,
      "text": "researchers come from a university in Boston,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215220.0,
      "end_time": 217716.0,
      "text": "and they take blood from us and our children"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217740.0,
      "end_time": 220380.0,
      "text": "for a research project focused on finding the gene."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 221180.0,
      "end_time": 222556.0,
      "text": "A few days later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222580.0,
      "end_time": 224996.0,
      "text": "researchers come from a medical center in New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225200.0,
      "end_time": 226540.0,
      "text": "and say they want blood, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227340.0,
      "end_time": 228740.0,
      "text": "\"These are children."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229380.0,
      "end_time": 231476.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re five and seven years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231500.0,
      "end_time": 233500.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t make them face the needle twice."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234180.0,
      "end_time": 237220.0,
      "text": "Go and get your share from the other researchers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240476.0,
      "text": "They laugh, incredulous."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240500.0,
      "end_time": 241700.0,
      "text": "\"Share?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243200.0,
      "end_time": 247420.0,
      "text": "It is then that we learn that there is little sharing in biomedical research."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248340.0,
      "end_time": 251360.0,
      "text": "This moment, more than any other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 251600.0,
      "end_time": 253700.0,
      "text": "lit a fire beneath my husband Pat and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 255460.0,
      "end_time": 257636.0,
      "text": "Pat and I went to a medical school library"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 257660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260620.00000000003,
      "text": "and we copied every article we could find on PXE."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 261540.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263500.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t understand a thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 264660.0,
      "end_time": 267396.0,
      "text": "We bought medical dictionaries and scientific textbooks"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 267420.0,
      "end_time": 269563.0,
      "text": "and read everything we could get our hands on."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 270380.0,
      "end_time": 272236.0,
      "text": "And though we still didn&#39;t understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274116.0,
      "text": "we could see patterns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274140.0,
      "end_time": 277515.0,
      "text": "and it became quickly apparent within a month"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 277540.0,
      "end_time": 281500.0,
      "text": "that there was no systematic effort to understand PXE."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 282820.0,
      "end_time": 284360.0,
      "text": "In addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284600.0,
      "end_time": 287300.0,
      "text": "the lack of sharing that we experienced was pervasive."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288300.0,
      "end_time": 290580.0,
      "text": "Researchers competed with each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 291460.0,
      "end_time": 295500.0,
      "text": "because the ecosystem was designed to reward competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 296380.0,
      "end_time": 298340.0,
      "text": "rather than to alleviate suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 299660.0,
      "end_time": 304676.0,
      "text": "We realized that we would have to do work on this condition ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304700.0,
      "end_time": 308219.0,
      "text": "to find solutions for ourselves and others like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309380.0,
      "end_time": 311716.0,
      "text": "But we faced two major barriers."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 311740.0,
      "end_time": 313236.0,
      "text": "The first one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315620.0,
      "text": "Pat and I have no science background."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 316740.0,
      "end_time": 320156.0,
      "text": "At the time, he&#39;s the manager of a construction company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 320180.0,
      "end_time": 324360.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m a former college chaplain stay-at-home mom --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 324600.0,
      "end_time": 327700.0,
      "text": "hardly the backgrounds to take the research world by storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 329300.0,
      "end_time": 330980.0,
      "text": "The second barrier:"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 332180.0,
      "end_time": 333660.0,
      "text": "researchers don&#39;t share."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334820.0,
      "end_time": 337340.0,
      "text": "People told us you can&#39;t herd cats."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 338460.0,
      "end_time": 341996.0,
      "text": "Well, yes you can if you move their food."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342200.0,
      "end_time": 344600.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345220.0,
      "end_time": 348780.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349220.0,
      "end_time": 352220.0,
      "text": "DNA and clinical data is the food."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 352780.0,
      "end_time": 355916.0,
      "text": "So we would collect blood and medical histories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 355940.0,
      "end_time": 359516.0,
      "text": "and require that all scientists using these resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 359540.0,
      "end_time": 363220.0,
      "text": "would share results with each other and with the people who donated."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 364900.0,
      "end_time": 367116.0,
      "text": "Well before the internet was in common use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367140.0,
      "end_time": 369996.0,
      "text": "Pat and I established PXE International,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 370200.0,
      "end_time": 374916.0,
      "text": "a nonprofit dedicated to initiating research and conducting it on PXE"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 374940.0,
      "end_time": 378420.0,
      "text": "and also supporting individuals with the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 379660.0,
      "end_time": 380996.0,
      "text": "Using traditional media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 381200.0,
      "end_time": 385436.0,
      "text": "we garnered around 100-150 people around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 385460.0,
      "end_time": 386715.0,
      "text": "who we asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 386740.0,
      "end_time": 389996.0,
      "text": "would you give us your blood, your tissue, your medical histories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 390200.0,
      "end_time": 391219.0,
      "text": "your medical records?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 392200.0,
      "end_time": 393859.0,
      "text": "And we brought all of that together."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 394740.0,
      "end_time": 398700.0,
      "text": "We quickly learned that this shared resource was not going to be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 399740.0,
      "end_time": 405760.0,
      "text": "And so we decided we had to do hardcore bench science --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 405100.0,
      "end_time": 406460.0,
      "text": "hardcore research."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 407220.0,
      "end_time": 409540.0,
      "text": "So we borrowed bench space at a lab at Harvard."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 410200.0,
      "end_time": 412796.0,
      "text": "A wonderful neighbor came a couple times a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 412820.0,
      "end_time": 416876.0,
      "text": "and sat with the kids from 8pm to 2am"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 416900.0,
      "end_time": 419236.0,
      "text": "while Pat and I extracted DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 420996.0,
      "text": "ran and scored gels"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 421200.0,
      "end_time": 422299.0,
      "text": "and searched for the gene."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423600.0,
      "end_time": 425540.0,
      "text": "Generous postdocs tutored us as we went along."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 426460.0,
      "end_time": 428659.0,
      "text": "Within a few years, we found the gene."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 429180.0,
      "end_time": 432196.0,
      "text": "We patented it so that it would be freely available."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 432220.0,
      "end_time": 434276.0,
      "text": "We created a diagnostic test."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 434300.0,
      "end_time": 436460.0,
      "text": "We put together a research consortium."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 437420.0,
      "end_time": 440620.0,
      "text": "We held research meetings and opened a center of excellence."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 441180.0,
      "end_time": 446556.0,
      "text": "We found more than 4,000 people around the world who had PXE,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 446580.0,
      "end_time": 448515.0,
      "text": "and held patient meetings"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 448540.0,
      "end_time": 451100.0,
      "text": "and did clinical trials and studies."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 452660.0,
      "end_time": 454156.0,
      "text": "Through all this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 454180.0,
      "end_time": 455460.0,
      "text": "we lived with fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 456860.0,
      "end_time": 459660.0,
      "text": "Fear of the disease breathing down our neck"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 461180.0,
      "end_time": 462500.0,
      "text": "while the clock ticked."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 463100.0,
      "end_time": 465260.0,
      "text": "Fear of researchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 466200.0,
      "end_time": 469859.0,
      "text": "so well credentialed and positioned in a world made for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 470740.0,
      "end_time": 473180.0,
      "text": "Fear that we were making the wrong choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 476596.0,
      "text": "Fear that the naysayers were right"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 476620.0,
      "end_time": 479740.0,
      "text": "and the cats would simply find a new food."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 480620.0,
      "end_time": 483796.0,
      "text": "But greater than all these fears was our drive to make a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 483820.0,
      "end_time": 486820.0,
      "text": "for our kids and for all those we had met along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 488100.0,
      "end_time": 489316.0,
      "text": "And very quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 489340.0,
      "end_time": 492750.0,
      "text": "we also realized what we were doing for one disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 492100.0,
      "end_time": 494220.0,
      "text": "we should do for all diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 496200.0,
      "end_time": 497835.0,
      "text": "We joined with, and I eventually led,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 497860.0,
      "end_time": 499760.0,
      "text": "Genetic Alliance --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 499100.0,
      "end_time": 501396.0,
      "text": "a network of health advocacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 501420.0,
      "end_time": 502636.0,
      "text": "patient advocacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 502660.0,
      "end_time": 504300.0,
      "text": "research and health organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 504980.0,
      "end_time": 507436.0,
      "text": "We built scalable and extensible resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 507460.0,
      "end_time": 510275.0,
      "text": "like biobanks and registries and directories of support"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 510300.0,
      "end_time": 511620.0,
      "text": "for all diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 512620.0,
      "end_time": 516676.0,
      "text": "And as I learned about all those diseases and all those disease communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 516700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519556.00000000006,
      "text": "I realized that there were two secrets in health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 519580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521380.00000000006,
      "text": "that were impacting me greatly."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 522299.0,
      "end_time": 523555.0,
      "text": "The first:"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 523580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526996.0,
      "text": "there are no ready answers for people like my kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 527200.0,
      "end_time": 528954.0,
      "text": "or all the people I was working with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 528979.0,
      "end_time": 531200.0,
      "text": "whether common or rare conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 531739.0,
      "end_time": 532979.0,
      "text": "And the second secret:"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 533580.0,
      "end_time": 537676.0,
      "text": "the answers lie in all of us together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537700.0,
      "end_time": 539180.0,
      "text": "donating our data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 540600.0,
      "end_time": 542356.0,
      "text": "our biological samples"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 542380.0,
      "end_time": 544100.0,
      "text": "and ultimately ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 546260.0,
      "end_time": 549596.0,
      "text": "There is a small groundswell of individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 549620.0,
      "end_time": 551876.0,
      "text": "who are working to change this."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 551900.0,
      "end_time": 554956.0,
      "text": "Citizen scientists, activists, hacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 554980.0,
      "end_time": 558156.0,
      "text": "who are using crowdsourcing, do-it-yourself science"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 558180.0,
      "end_time": 559380.0,
      "text": "are changing the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 560420.0,
      "end_time": 563339.0,
      "text": "Even President Obama and Vice President Biden"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 564500.0,
      "end_time": 566196.0,
      "text": "are evangelists for the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 566220.0,
      "end_time": 568700.0,
      "text": "that people should be partners in research."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 569500.0,
      "end_time": 572100.0,
      "text": "This is a founding principle of our organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 572780.0,
      "end_time": 574915.0,
      "text": "Sure, it&#39;s really hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 574940.0,
      "end_time": 578140.0,
      "text": "to discover and develop interventions and therapies."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 579300.0,
      "end_time": 581636.0,
      "text": "The science is hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 581660.0,
      "end_time": 583939.0,
      "text": "the regulatory regime is difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 584780.0,
      "end_time": 587795.0,
      "text": "There are a lot of stakeholders with lots of interests"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 587820.0,
      "end_time": 592100.0,
      "text": "and misaligned incentives like publishing, promotion and tenure."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 593180.0,
      "end_time": 596596.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t fault scientists for following this path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596620.0,
      "end_time": 599460.0,
      "text": "but I challenge them and us to do this differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 600220.0,
      "end_time": 603380.0,
      "text": "To recognize that people are at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 605220.0,
      "end_time": 606996.0,
      "text": "Genetic Alliance has experimented"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 607200.0,
      "end_time": 610500.0,
      "text": "in what it will take to transform these crusty systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 612740.0,
      "end_time": 614980.0,
      "text": "Our goal is to work without boundaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 615700.0,
      "end_time": 618820.0,
      "text": "That sounds abstract, but for us it&#39;s quite practical."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 621220.0,
      "end_time": 624916.0,
      "text": "When we&#39;re frustrated that entities won&#39;t share data --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 624940.0,
      "end_time": 630360.0,
      "text": "data that comes from people who gave their energy, their time, their blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 630600.0,
      "end_time": 631579.0,
      "text": "and even their tears --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 632340.0,
      "end_time": 633956.0,
      "text": "we need to stop and ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 633980.0,
      "end_time": 637100.0,
      "text": "\"How is it true that we could share, but we aren&#39;t?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 637660.0,
      "end_time": 639180.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re part of this system, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 646380.0,
      "text": "How do we make it so that people can share ideas freely?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 647220.0,
      "end_time": 651700.0,
      "text": "So that people can take risks and move closer to one another?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 653300.0,
      "end_time": 656555.0,
      "text": "This leads to a dissolving of us versus them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 656580.0,
      "end_time": 659940.0,
      "text": "not only for organizations but also for individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 660540.0,
      "end_time": 663915.0,
      "text": "If I&#39;m going to ask organizations or individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663940.0,
      "end_time": 666156.0,
      "text": "to strive for these standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 666180.0,
      "end_time": 671600.0,
      "text": "then I too need to explore my own being and my practices."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 671940.0,
      "end_time": 675196.0,
      "text": "If I&#39;m going to ask clinicians and researchers and administrators"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 675220.0,
      "end_time": 676796.0,
      "text": "to take risks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 676820.0,
      "end_time": 679820.0,
      "text": "then I, Sharon, need to take risks as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 680660.0,
      "end_time": 683500.0,
      "text": "I need to face my personal fears."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 684500.0,
      "end_time": 687380.0,
      "text": "My fear of not having enough impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 689220.0,
      "end_time": 691700.0,
      "text": "My fear of not leading well."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 692820.0,
      "end_time": 695740.0,
      "text": "My fear of not being enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 698540.0,
      "end_time": 702476.0,
      "text": "Just before they entered their teens, our kids stopped us in our tracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 702500.0,
      "end_time": 706196.0,
      "text": "and said, \"You have to stop worrying about making a difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 706220.0,
      "end_time": 707476.0,
      "text": "making an impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 707500.0,
      "end_time": 711476.0,
      "text": "and instead, like us, learn to live with disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 711500.0,
      "end_time": 713380.0,
      "text": "rather than fight it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 716420.0,
      "end_time": 717716.0,
      "text": "I have to ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 717740.0,
      "end_time": 719980.0,
      "text": "where does all my fear come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 721140.0,
      "end_time": 724900.0,
      "text": "The kids&#39; declaration shines a spotlight on that fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 725580.0,
      "end_time": 728660.0,
      "text": "It arises from a bedrock of love."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 729740.0,
      "end_time": 732300.0,
      "text": "I love Elizabeth and Ian."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 734140.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "I love people with PXE."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 737340.0,
      "end_time": 739460.0,
      "text": "I love people with any disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 740540.0,
      "end_time": 741740.0,
      "text": "I love people."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 744340.0,
      "end_time": 748956.0,
      "text": "Some of my colleagues have discovered that it is not death we fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 748980.0,
      "end_time": 751180.0,
      "text": "it is the enormity of our loving."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 752580.0,
      "end_time": 757356.0,
      "text": "This expansive love opens me to great pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 757380.0,
      "end_time": 759100.0,
      "text": "as I face loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 760860.0,
      "end_time": 763220.0,
      "text": "As I discover my fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 763980.0,
      "end_time": 765756.0,
      "text": "I discover that I"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 765780.0,
      "end_time": 767396.0,
      "text": "and all those around me"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 767420.0,
      "end_time": 770140.0,
      "text": "have boundless capacity for love."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 773460.0,
      "end_time": 774860.0,
      "text": "And I also discover"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 776600.0,
      "end_time": 777660.0,
      "text": "as I move into this fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 779220.0,
      "end_time": 781676.0,
      "text": "that I can learn many new things"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 781700.0,
      "end_time": 783600.0,
      "text": "and find paths"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 784140.0,
      "end_time": 787996.0,
      "text": "to things like practical solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 788200.0,
      "end_time": 791180.0,
      "text": "as well as the core of healing and health."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 794820.0,
      "end_time": 798380.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t fear fear the way I used to."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 800380.0,
      "end_time": 805516.0,
      "text": "In fact lately, with enormous support from all my fellow journeyers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 805540.0,
      "end_time": 808860.0,
      "text": "I notice that it&#39;s not a warning the way it used to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 809860.0,
      "end_time": 812716.0,
      "text": "I notice that instead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 812740.0,
      "end_time": 814636.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an invitation to go forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 814660.0,
      "end_time": 817900.0,
      "text": "because in it lies love and the path to greater love."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 819460.0,
      "end_time": 823600.0,
      "text": "If I turn with gentle curiosity toward that fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 824620.0,
      "end_time": 829676.0,
      "text": "I find enormous wealth within myself and others"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 829700.0,
      "end_time": 833200.0,
      "text": "and the ability to step into challenges that I never thought I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 834780.0,
      "end_time": 837140.0,
      "text": "My kids are ahead of me on that path still."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 838180.0,
      "end_time": 840750.0,
      "text": "At ages 29 and 27,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 840100.0,
      "end_time": 842556.0,
      "text": "they declare they are happy and healthy"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 842580.0,
      "end_time": 847700.0,
      "text": "despite having manifestations of PXE in their skin and eyes and arteries."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 848980.0,
      "end_time": 852316.0,
      "text": "And so I invite you, us, we,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 852340.0,
      "end_time": 853916.0,
      "text": "to turn toward our fear;"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 853940.0,
      "end_time": 856876.0,
      "text": "to embrace the things that scare us"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 856900.0,
      "end_time": 859360.0,
      "text": "and find the love at the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 859600.0,
      "end_time": 861276.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll not only find ourselves there"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 861300.0,
      "end_time": 865276.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;ll also be able to step into the shoes of those we fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 865300.0,
      "end_time": 866660.0,
      "text": "and those who fear us."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 867260.0,
      "end_time": 869340.0,
      "text": "If we breathe into that fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 870380.0,
      "end_time": 875360.0,
      "text": "and are vulnerable with the systems and people who challenge us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 875600.0,
      "end_time": 879140.0,
      "text": "our power as changemakers grows exponentially."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 880220.0,
      "end_time": 881476.0,
      "text": "And when we realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 881500.0,
      "end_time": 885156.0,
      "text": "that working on our inner life is working on our outer life"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 885180.0,
      "end_time": 887915.0,
      "text": "and outer work is inner work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 887940.0,
      "end_time": 890760.0,
      "text": "we get down to what is real"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 890100.0,
      "end_time": 891516.0,
      "text": "and shit gets done."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 891540.0,
      "end_time": 892996.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 893200.0,
      "end_time": 896836.0,
      "text": "There is no limit to what we can accomplish together."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 896860.0,
      "end_time": 898760.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 898100.0,
      "end_time": 900660.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}